summary: An Ordinance appropriating the sum of One Thousand Four Hundred Twenty-six and 88/100 (1426.88) Dollars, or so much thereof as may be necessary to be paid into Local Improvement District No. 1600 fund to reimburse said fund for deficiency caused by cancellation of assessment on Lots Four (4), Five (5) and Six (6), Block 104, D. T. Denny's 1st Addition to The City of Seattle.
